//Left Ventricle - Late Gd-Enhancement

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Cardio MRI

When I select 'Late Gd-Enhancement' checkbox
Then 'Finding' tab is enabled and selected by default
And 'Reference image' tab is enabled but not selected
And 'Result' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Segmental' from 'Result' dropdown menu
Then 'Localization' is enabled

When I select 'Non-Segmental'  from 'Result' dropdown menu
Then 'Distribution' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Focal' from 'Distribution' dropdown menu
Then 'Localization' is enabled